thread.title: Tyra Williams
thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by Tyra Williams

author: Tyra Williams
title: Tyra Williams
text: I had not intended on buying a dress when I went to Peaches. However, when I saw all those beautiful dresses I could not help myself. Those dresses were amazing and I love the choice I mad. The associate who helped me was really nice, and I loved the attention she gave to find the perfect dress for me.
